alTexture?: string;\n  selectedTexture?: string;\n  normalColor?: number;\n  sel
ectedColor?: number;\n  onChange?: (key: string, index: number) => void;\n  dept
h?: number;\n}\n```\n\nThe implementation adds `selectedKey`, `width`, `height`,
